Seeing #Skirball fire near the @GettyMuseum and @UCLA reminds me of the 1961 Bel-Air fire. Have we learned any lessons? Sure, but we're not applying it. Our opportunity for prevention is before the fire, suppression is almost impossible with large blazes. http://www. latimes.com/visuals/photog raphy/la-me-fw-archives-the-1961-bel-air-brush-fire-20170419-story.html … pic.twitter.com/AweAfCAT4f
